-- KUWAIT; MILITARY CONFRONTATIONS; IRAQ -- ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; UNITED 
STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- PERSIAN GULF; BUSH, GEORGE; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN 
RELATIONS -- IRAQ 
</P>
