RELATIONS -- ISRAEL; UNITED NATIONS -- ISRAEL; SHAMIR, YITZHAK; ISRAEL -- 
GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; ISRAEL -- TERRITORIES AND POSSESSIONS; UNITED STATES -- 
FOREIGN POLICY -- MIDDLE EAST 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
