<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA101690-0054 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 293012 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 16, 1990, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
