<P>
Business; Part D; Page 2A; Column 2; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
26 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
PEOPLE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Ronald P. Bird, president and chief executive officer of The Bank of Southern 
California, has been elected president of Episcopal Community Services. 
</P>
</TEXT>
