<P>
Grossmont Bank has named Debra A. Dvorak, commercial loan officer, Anna Holmes, 
assistant vice president and operations officer, Alan J. McEachern, vice 
president and manager, Sharon E. Murray, vice president/business development, 
Patrick M. Saunders, vice president and manager and Thomas E. Swanson, senior 
vice president and North County administrator. 
