</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Valencia-based Camera Platforms International Inc. and a subsidiary of UST 
Inc., formerly U.S. Tobacco, have agreed in principle to a stock-for-debt swap, 
which calls for UST to cancel the debt owed to it by Camera Platforms in 
exchange for shares of Camera Platforms' common stock. 
</P>
