industries, owes UST $11.5 million. Under the agreement, the debt will be 
exchanged for 8.83 million Camera Platforms shares at $1.30 per share. After 
the swap, UST would own 9.43 million Camera Platforms shares, or 76% of the 
total outstanding. 
</P>
<P>
UST also holds an option to purchase 500,000 shares of Camera Platforms stock 
owned by a principal shareholder. 
