<P>
LAKERS SIGN UP IRVING THOMAS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Wire Services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Forward Irving Thomas, a rookie free agent from Florida State University, was 
added to the Lakers' preseason roster today. 
</P>
<P>
The 6-foot-8 Thomas was a member of the Lakers summer league squad. He averaged 
17.1 points and 8.8 rebounds during the team's 10-game schedule. 
</P>
<P>
As a senior at Florida State, Thomas averaged 16.7 points and 7.6 rebounds per 
game. 
</P>
