SABATINI A WINNER IN GERMANY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Wire Services 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
FILDERSTADT, Germany 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Top-seeded Gabriela Sabatini of Argentina defeated France's Julie Halard, 6-4, 
6-3, today in the women's Porsche Grand Prix tournament. 
</P>
<P>
Rosalyn Fairbank of the United States came from behind to beat Germany's Katja 
Oeljeklaus, 1-6, 6-4, 6-4, and Argentina's Mercedes Paz overcame Heike Thoms of 
Germany, 7-6, 6-1. 
</P>
<P>
Fifth-seeded Jana Novotna of Czechoslovakia defeated Pascale Etchemendy of 
France, 6-4, 6-0. 
</P>
